message.body: Hey beautiful. I'd like to see you tonight. Interested in watching the oscars? Say around nine?
i thought we were planning to hang out tomorrow night instead, because i have a midterm tomorrow?
Oh yes that's right. How's the studying going?
i haven't really started yet. i mostly worked and napped today (low on sleep). but after i'm done with this church thing i'm actually going to study...
Well have fun and good luck. I'll see you tomorrow.
thanks. sorry i couldn't see you tonight! enjoy the oscars. :)
hey, i need to be on campus from 9 to 10:30, do you still want to hang out or is that too inconvenient?
it was good! no bible q's but i did get other stuff. i feel bad wasting your texts...
You're not wasting them. Sweet dreams.
